#Rewrite Programming Exercise 1.11 to prompt the user to enter the number of years and displays the population after that many years. 
#Use the hint in Programming Exercise 1.11 for this program.

years = int(input("Enter the number of years: "))

population = 312032486 + years * 365 * 24 * 60 * 60 / 7 - years * 365 * 24 * 60 * 60 / 13 + years * 365 * 24 * 60 * 60 / 45

print("The population in", years, "years is", int(population + 1))
